provenance.p:
On fol. 11v, a monogram consisting of the letters G and Þ is written in the upper margin four times. According to Kålund (
) this is the monogram of the bishop of Hólar Guðbrandur Þorláksson. Ólafur Halldórsson (
83, footnote 17 ) however, finds that the initials belong to Gísli Þórðarson.
